translate spanish strings:

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:2
    old "Amber's Grandpa's favorite tape, and now it's her favorite. I guess that means it's my favorite, too, since it's so important to Amber. I was even lucky enough to hear some of it live, at the festival we went to together."
    new "Amber's Grandpa's favorite tape, and now it's her favorite. I guess that means it's my favorite, too, since it's so important to Amber. I was even lucky enough to hear some of it live, at the festival we went to together."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:3
    old "Buying this slushie was the first nice thing Amber ever did for me. Well, second, since she gave me a ride there, too. It's cola-flavored, since they never had that flavor in my hometown."
    new "Buying this slushie was the first nice thing Amber ever did for me. Well, second, since she gave me a ride there, too. It's cola-flavored, since they never had that flavor in my hometown."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:4
    old "The book that started everything! It contains riddles with locations to all of the miner's hidden treasure. Without this, I would've never met Amber…"
    new "The book that started everything! It contains riddles with locations to all of the miner's hidden treasure. Without this, I would've never met Amber…"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:5
    old "This belongs to Joe, but Mariah's the one who spends the most time thinking about it. I guess it's an old family heirloom. It's how Mariah says she knew about the treasure before anyone else."
    new "This belongs to Joe, but Mariah's the one who spends the most time thinking about it. I guess it's an old family heirloom. It's how Mariah says she knew about the treasure before anyone else."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:6
    old "One of Tess's most treasured possessions. She collects license plates and puts them together like this. She said that someday, she'll give me one of her windchimes to keep!"
    new "One of Tess's most treasured possessions. She collects license plates and puts them together like this. She said that someday, she'll give me one of her windchimes to keep!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:7
    old "Amber and I ate this at a diner together. She thought I was weird for dipping my fries in a milkshake! She didn't know that everyone does that."
    new "Amber and I ate this at a diner together. She thought I was weird for dipping my fries in a milkshake! She didn't know that everyone does that."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:8
    old "We borrowed this from Mariah, and kinda never gave it back. But that's double fair, since she did the same thing with my brother's car."
    new "We borrowed this from Mariah, and kinda never gave it back. But that's double fair, since she did the same thing with my brother's car."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:9
    old "These are what the old miner hid his treasure in. We found a few of them along the way."
    new "These are what the old miner hid his treasure in. We found a few of them along the way."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:10
    old "Gold! Real, honest to God gold! At first, I couldn't believe it either."
    new "Gold! Real, honest to God gold! At first, I couldn't believe it either."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:11
    old "I kept this with me for most of our trip! It has some of our best memories together. I may have gone a little overboard sometimes though, like when we saw the World's Tallest Thermometer."
    new "I kept this with me for most of our trip! It has some of our best memories together. I may have gone a little overboard sometimes though, like when we saw the World's Tallest Thermometer."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:12
    old "Okay, so, growing up I would always get super frustrated when I saw other kids coloring outside the lines. It’s like, “Why can’t you slow down and stay in the lines? It’s not that hard! It’ll look prettier! You’ll be happier! It doesn’t look right! AGH!” Anyway, I have a girlfriend now."
    new "Okay, so, growing up I would always get super frustrated when I saw other kids coloring outside the lines. It’s like, “Why can’t you slow down and stay in the lines? It’s not that hard! It’ll look prettier! You’ll be happier! It doesn’t look right! AGH!” Anyway, I have a girlfriend now."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:13
    old "“You’re toast.” When Amber made that pun, I groaned. But the truth is, I was actually thinking about doing the same thing. Fortunately, I ended up making a better one."
    new "“You’re toast.” When Amber made that pun, I groaned. But the truth is, I was actually thinking about doing the same thing. Fortunately, I ended up making a better one."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:14
    old "“Sam-I-Amber” is still the proudest I’ve ever been of a joke. Amber was always so grumpy when we first met, those eggs may as well have been a portrait!"
    new "“Sam-I-Amber” is still the proudest I’ve ever been of a joke. Amber was always so grumpy when we first met, those eggs may as well have been a portrait!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:15
    old "My favorite breakfast in the world. The pancakes were chocolate and had chocolate chips, and the chocolate milk was homemade. Can you tell that I like chocolate?"
    new "My favorite breakfast in the world. The pancakes were chocolate and had chocolate chips, and the chocolate milk was homemade. Can you tell that I like chocolate?"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:16
    old "Arches National Park is so pretty! I wish we could have spent more time sightseeing than sitting in traffic. It’s weird, though. This brochure doesn’t mention Chip Off the Old Block, so I’m not sure how Amber knew about it…"
    new "Arches National Park is so pretty! I wish we could have spent more time sightseeing than sitting in traffic. It’s weird, though. This brochure doesn’t mention Chip Off the Old Block, so I’m not sure how Amber knew about it…"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:18
    old "Mariah ate, like, an entire cow, and I’m pretty sure that still wasn’t enough because I saw her picking at Tess’ tendies, too."
    new "Mariah ate, like, an entire cow, and I’m pretty sure that still wasn’t enough because I saw her picking at Tess’ tendies, too."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:21
    old "My heart skipped two whole beats when Amber asked me to go to the festival with her! It was the first time I really felt like her girlfriend. "
    new "My heart skipped two whole beats when Amber asked me to go to the festival with her! It was the first time I really felt like her girlfriend. "

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:24
    old "Gained five pounds. Don’t care. Would do it again."
    new "Gained five pounds. Don’t care. Would do it again."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:25
    old "Everything in the motorhome move around so much when we’re driving, so I glued velcro on the bottom of this to keep it from sliding off the shelf. My heart would be so sad if it broke."
    new "Everything in the motorhome move around so much when we’re driving, so I glued velcro on the bottom of this to keep it from sliding off the shelf. My heart would be so sad if it broke."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:26
    old "Amber got these for me our first time in Vegas! They ended up melting together, so we just had a big chain of gummies. We ended up making a kissing game out of it, but I think it would’ve worked better with spaghetti."
    new "Amber got these for me our first time in Vegas! They ended up melting together, so we just had a big chain of gummies. We ended up making a kissing game out of it, but I think it would’ve worked better with spaghetti."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:27
    old "Amber was right, this is totally my jam. Speaking of jam, this would be amazing with strawberry jelly on top."
    new "Amber was right, this is totally my jam. Speaking of jam, this would be amazing with strawberry jelly on top."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:28
    old "Amber got this at the same place where I got the pancakes. She might make fun of me, but at least I didn't order half the menu!"
    new "Amber got this at the same place where I got the pancakes. She might make fun of me, but at least I didn't order half the menu!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:30
    old "My big sister used to have a phone like this! I remember being soooo jealous, but looking at it now, it sorta looks like a toy."
    new "My big sister used to have a phone like this! I remember being soooo jealous, but looking at it now, it sorta looks like a toy."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:31
    old "I got this after me and Amber went to the music festival! My dad would flip if her knew this, but I’m kinda glad Mariah sold my old phone. I dropped it in the bathtub so many times."
    new "I got this after me and Amber went to the music festival! My dad would flip if her knew this, but I’m kinda glad Mariah sold my old phone. I dropped it in the bathtub so many times."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:33

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:35
    old "Amber’s alien looks so dorky, but I love it because it reminds me of her! Cassi’s looks so much nicer than mine, though. Hmph!"
    new "Amber’s alien looks so dorky, but I love it because it reminds me of her! Cassi’s looks so much nicer than mine, though. Hmph!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:38
    old "The rainforest café was AWESOME, and sharing a dessert with Amber was the best part! I already know where I want to go for our anniversary!"
    new "The rainforest café was AWESOME, and sharing a dessert with Amber was the best part! I already know where I want to go for our anniversary!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:39
    old "This is the license plate Mariah picked up for Tess during the convention. Amber doesn’t believe me, but I think Mariah is a really thoughtful person!"
    new "This is the license plate Mariah picked up for Tess during the convention. Amber doesn’t believe me, but I think Mariah is a really thoughtful person!"

