    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:38
    old "These are what Tess was eating when we ran into her in Moab. There are so many of them, I bet that Mariah ordered a large size just so she can steal some."
    new "These are what Tess was eating when we ran into her in Moab. There are so many of them, I bet that Mariah ordered a large size just so she can steal some."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:40
    old "Joe's meal of choice in Utah. Doesn't it remind you of him? A grilled cheese and tomato soup isn't the most exciting thing, but it's trusty and reliable!"
    new "Joe's meal of choice in Utah. Doesn't it remind you of him? A grilled cheese and tomato soup isn't the most exciting thing, but it's trusty and reliable!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:41
    old "Not that there's anything wrong with these, but those fries would totally go better with a milkshake too."
    new "Not that there's anything wrong with these, but those fries would totally go better with a milkshake too."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:43
    old "Later on, Amber told me that she covered all her food groups in this meal: steak, chicken, pork, seafood and \"everything else.\""
    new "Later on, Amber told me that she covered all her food groups in this meal: steak, chicken, pork, seafood and \"everything else.\""

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:44
    old "I can't believe she went back for {i}more{/i}. She might be the only person I know who gets her money's worth out of a buffet."
    new "I can't believe she went back for {i}more{/i}. She might be the only person I know who gets her money's worth out of a buffet."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:50
    old "We got this portrait drawn of us the first time we went to Las Vegas... Maybe it isn't the most flattering pic ever, but it was fun, so who cares?"
    new "We got this portrait drawn of us the first time we went to Las Vegas... Maybe it isn't the most flattering pic ever, but it was fun, so who cares?"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:53
    old "Somehow, I ended up losing another battle to Mariah in Las Vegas... At least this time, the real winner is Tess!"
    new "Somehow, I ended up losing another battle to Mariah in Las Vegas... At least this time, the real winner is Tess!"

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:55
    old "Totally an acquired taste, but not as bad as it sounds. Hopefully next time, we can share a glass with Cassi."
    new "Totally an acquired taste, but not as bad as it sounds. Hopefully next time, we can share a glass with Cassi."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:57
    old "Tess' phone. Well, I guess it's Mariah's phone, but I'm pretty sure Tess uses it more. Kinda surprised it doesn't have more cracks in it."
    new "Tess' phone. Well, I guess it's Mariah's phone, but I'm pretty sure Tess uses it more. Kinda surprised it doesn't have more cracks in it."

    # game/marinasthoughts.rpy:58
    old "The wallpaper was definitely Tess' choice. I wonder if she made it herself, because I can't think of anyone else who wants this."
    new "The wallpaper was definitely Tess' choice. I wonder if she made it herself, because I can't think of anyone else who wants this."

